                    Upload photos of bloodwork or metabolic panels. Vivral normalizes data against reference ranges and highlights anomalies instantly.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <span class="mono-tag acid">CAPABILITY 03</span>
                <h3>Clinical Synthesis</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    Vivral acts as an active scribe, synthesizing disjointed patient history into standard SOAP notes for professional review.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="showcase-row">
            <div class="showcase-visual">
                <div class="device-frame">
                    <img src="/IMG_1656-portrait.png" alt="Vivral Chat Interface">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="showcase-content">
                <span class="mono-tag">01 // REASONING ENGINE</span>
                <h2>The World's First<br>On-Device Medical AI.</h2>
                <p>
                    Powered by our proprietary NE.01R small-language model. Vivral doesn't just guess; it thinks. 
                    Processing complex diagnostics with zero latency, entirely on your local hardware. 
                    Designed for remote environments where cloud connectivity is impossible.
                </p>

                <div class="spec-table">
                    <div class="spec-row">
                        <span>MODEL ARCHITECTURE</span>
                        <span class="spec-val">TRANSFORMER (QUANTIZED)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-row">
                        <span>KNOWLEDGE BASE</span>
                        <span class="spec-val">UMLS / SNOMED-CT</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-row">
                        <span>LATENCY</span>
                        <span class="spec-val">< 12ms</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="showcase-row">
            <div class="showcase-content">
                <span class="mono-tag alert">02 // PRIVACY ARCHITECTURE</span>
                <h2 style="color: var(--neon-clay);" class="text-glow-clay">The Patient Passport.</h2>
                <p>
                    Your health data is yours. The NE Medical Passport utilizes Apple's Secure Enclave to encrypt biomarkers locally.
                    Vivral operates in a complete sandbox. No information is ever trained on, and no data ever leaves your phone.
                </p>

                <div class="spec-table">
                    <div class="spec-row">
                        <span>ENCRYPTION STANDARD</span>
                        <span class="spec-val secure">AES-256 (LOCAL)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-row">
                        <span>CLOUD UPLOADS</span>
                        <span class="spec-val secure">BLOCKED</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-row">
                        <span>COMPLIANCE</span>
                        <span class="spec-val secure">HIPAA / GDPR READY</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="showcase-visual" style="border-left: var(--border-tech);">
                <div class="device-frame">
                    <img src="/IMG_1657-left.png" alt="Patient Passport Interface">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="showcase-row">
            <div class="showcase-content" style="border-right: var(--border-tech);">
                <span class="mono-tag">03 // MISSION</span>
                <h2 style="color: var(--neon-cyan);">Democratizing<br>Survival.</h2>
                <p>
                    World-class healthcare is currently a privilege of geography and wealth. Nair Engineering is building systems to make high-fidelity medical guidance accessible to every human on Earth, regardless of internet access or income.
                </p>
                <button class="hud-btn" style="margin-top: 2rem; width: fit-content;">READ THE WHITEPAPER</button>
            </div>
        
            <div class="showcase-visual" style="border-left: none;">
                <div class="device-frame">
                    <img src="/IMG_1659.jpeg" alt="Medical Analysis View">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;">
                <div class="brand">NAIR ENGINEERING</div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 1rem; color: #555;">
                    &copy; 2025 Nair Engineering LLC.<br>
                    Glen Ridge, NJ / Gainesville, FL
                </p>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: flex-end;">
                <nav class="footer-links">
                    <a href="#">Privacy</a>
                    <a href="#">Terms</a>
                    <a href="#">Twitter</a>
                    <a href="#">Contact</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </footer>

    </main>

</body>
